    <string name="header_faq_whatshare">What is share?</string>
    <string name="note_faq_whatshare">Shares are your primary means of attacking and defending in Plutocrat. You can buy other players out of the game by challenging them to match your buyout offer (some number of shares).\n\nIf someone else attempts to buy you out, you have to match their buyout offer with an equal number of shares in order to stay in the game.</string>
    <string name="header_faq_moreshare">What if I don\'t have enough shares to match a buyout?</string>
    <string name="note_faq_moreshare">Everyone starts with 1 share. If you need more, navigate to the Shares view via the bottom navigation bar to purchase more.</string>
